                 <h3><strong>Carwood  Accountancy Limited - PRIVACY POLICY</strong></h3> 
                 <p>By &lsquo;We&rsquo; or &lsquo;Us&rsquo;, We mean Carwood Accountancy<strong> </strong>Limited (&ldquo;Carwood Accountancy&rdquo;). By &ldquo;You&rdquo; We mean the client who  has accessed our service. We are Registered in England and Wales. Registered  Address: Carwood Accountancy<strong> </strong>Limited, Express Networks 3, 6 Oldham Road, Manchester, M4 5DB Company  Number: <strong>10782318</strong>. &quot;Tax  Allowance Awareness&quot; is the trading names or styles of Carwood  Accountancy<strong> </strong>Limited.</p>
                 <ul>
                   <li><strong>WHAT  IS THE PURPOSE OF THIS PRIVACY NOTICE</strong><strong>? </strong></li>
                 </ul>
