                 <ul>
                   <li><strong>WHO IS THE DATA CONTROLLER? </strong></li>
                 </ul>
                 <p>We are the controller and We are responsible for your  personal information. We are not required to appoint a Data Protection Officer  (DPO). If you have any questions relating to this Privacy Policy or Notice,  including any requests to exercise your legal rights (as explained in section 13),  please use the contact information below</p>
