                 <p>Ordinarily, We do  not rely on pure consent as a legal basis for processing data other than in  relation to sending marketing communications to you via email or text message.  You have the right to withdraw consent at any time by contacting us using the  above contact information in Section 3 of this Privacy Policy. </p>
